Blockade of growth hormone (GH), decreased insulin-like growth factor-1 (IGF1) 
action and increased insulin sensitivity are associated with life extension and 
an apparent slowing of the aging process. We examined expression of genes 
involved in insulin action, IR, IRS1, IRS2, IGF1, IGF1R, GLUT4, PPARs and RXRs 
